data.text: As of our favourite medias in Britain, if they have in your targets, then be really careful, they don't even care that you are a human being like everyone else. Personally, I don't care what they think anymore. I stand by #JoseMourinho 👊🏻👊🏻👊🏻 https://t.co/XbehKwKqrZ

Some don't understand how lucky they are; having the chance to go to games, watching Manchester United play week in week out LIVE. Mind you, if I had the chance, while everyone's so hurt from that defeat, I'd go and watch them v Burnley.
